<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Hacked</title>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: url('https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Arar_Saudi_Arabia.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
        background-size: cover;
        color: #00ff00;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    body::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
    }

    .center {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        text-align: center;
        z-index: 2;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 60px;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ff00, 0 0 20px #00ff00;
        animation: glitch 1s infinite;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 20px;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }

    @keyframes glitch {
        0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skew(0deg); }
        20% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skew(5deg); }
        40% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skew(-5deg); }
        60% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skew(3deg); }
        80% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skew(-3deg); }
        100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) skew(0deg); }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="center">
    <h1>تم اختراقك</h1>
    <p>بواسطة خلود</p>
    <p>📍 ساكنه في عرعر</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
